Issues.Body:
This is a question about Bulma.

Overview of the problem
This is about the Bulma CSS framework

I'm using Bulma 0.7.4

Description of the problem:

I'm trying to use Bulma's handy mixins in my custom scss code, for example:

`.content-item {
  @include clearfix;
}`

However during compiling to css I get the error: "no mixin named clearfix".

I did add the utilities to my scss:
`@import "../node_modules/bulma/sass/utilities/_all.sass";`

Anyone know what i'm doing wrong?
